name: The Greatest Band Ever 24"x36" Screen Print
description: A 24" x 36" infographic print that answers the question, who is The Greatest Band Ever. It's the result of a KICKSTARTER project that allowed people to purchase the print and get a vote. it was crowd-funding and crowd-sourcing at it's best. There are a few prints left from the signed and numbered limited edition set of 400. Ships free within the US and will arrive in time for the Holidays if you're looking for a unique gift. Just order before Dec. 5th.
